BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-25T22:45:00&endDate=2026-06-26T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMILDMAY LINE: Monday 22\, Tuesday 23\, Wednesday 24 and Thursday 25 June\, after 2345 each evening\, no westbound service from Stratford to Camden Road. The 2359 and 0015 services from Stratford will start from Camden Road at 0018 and 0035. Customers should use the last westbound service from Stratford at 2344\, or local bus routes 30\, 274\, 388\, 393 or 488. In addition\, the 2300 Stratford to Richmond train will not run.
DTEND:20260626T002900Z
