DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-28T21:15:00&endDate=2026-06-29T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMILDMAY LINE: Sunday 28 June\, from 2215\, no service between Camden Road and Stratford. Rail replacement buses will run as follows: Service S: Camden Road - Holloway Road (for Piccadilly line) - Highbury & Islington - Canonbury - Dalston Junction (for Dalston Kingsland) - Hackney Central - Homerton - Hackney Wick - Stratford. For Caledonian Road & Barnsbury use local bus route 274 to/from Camden Road or walk to/from Highbury & Islington. Some buses continue on request westbound-only from Camden Road as follows: Camden Road - Kentish Town West - Gospel Oak (bus stop in Southampton Road) - Hampstead Heath - Finchley Road Tube (for Finchley Road & Frognal) - West Hampstead - Brondesbury (bus stops in Kilburn High Road) - Queen's Park (walk/local buses for Brondesbury Park) - Kensal Rise - Willesden Junction - Acton Central - South Acton - Gunnersbury - Kew Gardens (Royal Botanic Gardens) - Richmond. Last through trains: Richmond to Stratford 2126\; Camden Road to Stratford 2203\; Stratford to Richmond 2201\; Stratford to Clapham Junction 2208
